0.title: Warriors for Hire
0.plot: Prohyas and Vambre's Warrior service is open for business as they are tasked to unclog a royal sink.

1.title: Mushroom Menace
1.plot: The Mysterious Hooded Woman wants the Warriors For Hire to defend her giant pumpkin home from the dreaded Smashroom Mushroom, but Vambre and Prohyas can't complete their mission without help from Zombie Pumpkin Magisword!

2.title: The Mystery of Loch Mess
2.plot: Warriors For Hire are sent to Loch Mess to save a bunch of delivery people and become the go to adventurers for the kingdom.

3.title: Squirrelled Domination!
3.plot: Prohyas has to stay home to look after a sick Dolphin Magisword. As a result Vambre has to face her fear of squirrels to find a tree get retrieve five golden acorns.

4.title: Case Clothed
4.plot: Case Clothed: Princess Zange hires the Warriors to be her secret service for the afternoon to go shopping, but the looting pirates of Keelhaul Cove make fashion makeovers nearly impossible to manage. / Surely You Jest-O: House sitting for Omnibus is boring work for the Warriors, but their decision to allow Jest-O and his Taunting Jester Magisword come in from the rain to entertain them turns out to be their worst idea yet!

5.title: Surely You Jesto
5.plot: House sitting for Omnibus is boring work for the Warriors, but their decision to allow Jest-O and his Taunting Jester Magisword come in from the rain to entertain them turns out to be their worst idea yet.

6.title: Cleanliness Is Next to Grupliness
6.plot: Grup has been stinking up the entire town of Rhyboflaven, but no matter how the Warriors try to lead the little dragon to water, they can't make him bathe!

7.title: Flirty Phantom
7.plot: Lost in Transylberia, the Warriors come to a haunted house for help and meet a young ghost lady inside that wants to spend the rest of her afterlife with Prohyas.

8.title: The Wrath of Neddy
8.plot: Flirty Phantom: Lost in Transylberia, the Warriors come to a haunted house for help and meet a young ghost lady inside that wants to spend the rest of her afterlife with Prohyas! / The Wrath of Neddy: After Neddy the Mallet easily sails through all the obstacles in the Cave of Stuff he decides to stay as King Neddy, displacing the Cave Weirdos who beg the Warriors to help them reclaim their cave.

9.title: Working for Scales
9.plot: Princess Zange is sick and requires a dinosaur scale for a tea remedy, but King Rexxtopher is fiercely against the Warriors stepping foot inside his Dinosaur Kingdom to get it.

10.title: Felonious Prose
10.plot: Working for Scales: Princess Zange is sick and requires a dinosaur scale for a tea remedy, but King Rexxtopher is fiercely against the Warriors stepping foot inside his Dinosaur Kingdom to get it. / Felonious Prose: The Warrior mission of finding a lost contact lens gets seriously compromised from Vambre's obsession with the latest Veronica Victorious novel.

11.title: Potion in the Ocean
11.plot: Witchy Simone joins the Warriors on a mission deep in the Fickle Sea to find an eye of newt for her magic potion, but Man Fish the Fish Man won't them harm his sea newt pal!

12.title: Bad Bad Cop
12.plot: Vambre and Prohyas pretend to be cops in their attempts to shakedown a dangerous bunch of pirates to find a broccoli smuggler.

13.title: Gotta Get Grup to Get Down
13.plot: Gotta Get Grup to Get Down: Grup hires the Warriors to help him become the biggest music star in Rhyboflaven, yet helping the little dragon achieve his big dream is no small task. / Thick As Thieves: Phil the Pilferer robs Vambre and Prohyas of their very best Magiswords so he can snag the Sheepy Mantis, but the Warriors find out that no Magisword is lame as they manage to keep Phil from becoming Thief of the Year.

14.title: Thick as Thieves
14.plot: Phil the Pilferer robs Vambre and Prohyas of their very best Magiswords so he can snag the Sheepy Mantis, but the Warriors find out that no Magisword is lame as they manage to keep Phil from becoming Thief of the Year.

15.title: Biggest Fan
15.plot: An obsessed super fan goes to dangerous extremes just to be saved by her Warrior heroes: Vambre and Prohyas.

16.title: Dungeons and Dayjobs
16.plot: Biggest Fan: An obsessed super fan goes to dangerous extremes just to be saved by her Warrior heroes: Vambre and Prohyas. / Dungeons and Dayjobs: A botched mission leaves the Warriors in debt, so they take day jobs at Slugburger and sling Slugburgers for Witchy Simone!

17.title: Little Sword of Horrors
17.plot: Little Sword of Horrors: Prohyas grows a new Magisword from a tiny seed, but doesn't know that his Carnivorous Plant Magisword is a menace to Lyvsherian society until its too late! / Champions of Breakfast: An epic battle between Vambre and her Waffle Magisword and Prohyas' Pancake Magisword escalates to a war that can only end when Grup solicits his Cave Weirdo pals to be peacemakers.

18.title: Champions of Breakfast
18.plot: An epic battle between Vambre and her Waffle Magisword and Prohyas' Pancake Magisword escalates to a war that can only end when Grup solicits his Cave Weirdo pals to be peacemakers.

19.title: Gut Feelings
19.plot: With help from Zombie Pumpkin Magisword, the Warriors help get to the root of who stole all the vegetable Magiswords that belong to the angry bunny, Hoppus.

20.title: The Tome of Morrow
20.plot: The Tome of Morrow: Noville's Magisword training with Vambre pays off and the Warriors invite him on a mission to an ancient cave in the Barren Faceland to find the rare and sacred book, the Tome of Morrow. / Share and Share Dislike: Super Shooting Star Magisword is the coolest Magisword ever, but Vambre and Prohyas can't seem to share it, and even a quest to reclaim the never-melting ice cube back from Frosteratu can't shake their obsession.
